title._content: Besuch Se. Exzellenz Generalfeldmarschall von Eichhorn in Taganrog

description._content: Title: Besuch Se. Exzellenz Generalfeldmarschall von Eichhorn in Taganrog Alternative Title: The visit of His Excellency Field Marshal von Eichhorn to Taganrog Creator: Unknown Date: Spring 1918 Part Of: Der Vormarsch der Flieger Abteilung 27 in der Ukraine Place: Taganrog, Rostov Oblast, Russia Description: A photograph of General Field Marshal Hermann von Eichhorn inspecting troops during a visit to Taganrog. During this period, von Eichhorn was both supreme commander of Army Group Kiev and the German military governor of Ukraine. He was later assassinated in Kiev on July 30, 1918.
